ls0 ws0">faithful children of the Most High, of every age and clime, safe </div><div class="t mf65 xe h4 yf47 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">at home in the earth made new. </div><div class="t m1928 x92 h2c y1577 ff6 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON I.—Prophetic Outline of the Church till the </div><div class="t m862 x89 h2c y7e3 ff6 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">End. </div><div class="t m2d96 x6b h28 ya08 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">JULY 2, </div><div class="t m8a x1b h4 ya08 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1904. </div><div class="t m50e x32 h30 y5aa ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Questions. </div><div class="t m122c x14 h28 y804 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">i. What did the revelator behold in heaven? With </div><div class="t m13f x15 h28 y93f ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">what was the woman clothed? What was under her </div><div class="t m2a1 x92 h28 ya22 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">feet? What was upon her head? Rev. 12:T. Of what </div><div class="t m16ad x92 h28 y994 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is a woman a symbol? Ter. 6:2. Note I. </div><div class="t m8aa x18 h30 y132a ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The offerings for this quarter go to the most needy fields. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
